text: Andrew John Furey (born July 1975) is a Canadian orthopedic surgeon and politician. He became the 14th Premier of Newfoundland and Labrador on August 19, 2020. Furey is the Member of the House of Assembly for Humber-Gros Morne. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Premiers of Newfoundland and Labrador Category:Canadian physicians
